OL,3,CPetrol prices surge as the war in the
OL,4,CMiddle East impacts region
OL,6,FMotorists in Cumbria and south of
OL,7,FScotland have seen fuel prices rise
OL,8,Fwith one truck stop owner warning
OL,9,Fthere could be shortages.
OL,11,FFighting in the Middle East entered
OL,12,Fits sixth day today (Thursday), with
OL,13,Fthe conflict continuing to escalate as
OL,14,Fmilitary operations expand into
OL,15,Fneighbouring areas with increasing
OL,16,Faggression.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
