OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1772817082
OL,3,CPetrol prices surge as the war in the
OL,4,CMiddle East impacts region
OL,6,FAs a result, thousands of miles away
OL,7,Fback on home soil, fuel prices are
OL,8,Fgoing up as the war causes severe
OL,9,Fdisruption in the global flow of crude
OL,10,Foil.
OL,12,FAs well as affecting prices at the
OL,13,Fpump, if higher fuel costs persist
OL,14,Fthey could have knock-on effects on
OL,15,Fthe costs of other goods.
OL,17,FWhat increases are motorists seeing?
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
