CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1772817082
OL,3,CPetrol prices surge as the war in the
OL,4,CMiddle East impacts region
OL,6,FSince Saturday, when the war began,
OL,7,Fthe average price of petrol is up to
OL,8,F135.20p per litre - That's up by
OL,9,Fnearly 2.5p.
OL,11,FMeanwhile, the price of diesel is
OL,12,Fsitting at 145.66p per litre - that's
OL,13,Fa rise of more than 3p.
OL,15,FThe AA motoring group says that over
OL,16,Fthe next few weeks, the cost of fuel
OL,17,Fcould return to where they were at the
OL,18,Fstart of the year.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,357,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1772817082
OL,3,CPetrol prices surge as the war in the
OL,4,CMiddle East impacts region
OL,6,FThis would mean a change to the
OL,7,Ftrajectory of fuel prices we have seen
OL,8,Fso far, which have been falling in the
OL,9,FUK over the past few weeks.
OL,11,FFurther rises will depend on the
OL,12,Fmagnitude and duration of the conflict
OL,13,Fand there remains a huge amount of
OL,14,Funcertainty at this stage as to
OL,15,Fwhether the conflict will have a
OL,16,Flasting effect on the price of oil,
OL,17,Fgas and wider energy costs.
OL,19,FMeanwhile, UK Government says it's
OL,20,Fworking to support the UK's oil and
OL,21,Fgas supply.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,357,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1772817082
OL,3,CPetrol prices surge as the war in the
OL,4,CMiddle East impacts region
OL,6,FWhy are fuel prices being impacted?
OL,8,FThe far-reaching conflict is
OL,9,Fdisrupting the global flow of crude
OL,10,Foil, as the Strait of Hormuz, a major
OL,11,Fshipping route through which a fifth
OL,12,Fof global oil and gas supplies pass,
OL,13,Fwas caught in the middle of the
OL,14,Fconflict.
OL,16,FIran controls the entire northern side
OL,17,Fof the Strait, effectively allowing it
OL,18,Fto wield the Strait as a geopolitical
OL,19,Fchokepoint.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,357,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F356A1772817082
OL,3,CPetrol prices surge as the war in the
OL,4,CMiddle East impacts region
OL,6,FWhile the strait is officially open,
OL,7,Ftrade has dropped by 80 per cent since
OL,8,FSaturday.
OL,10,FIran has carried out attacks on
OL,11,Fpassing ships and vowed to continue to
OL,12,Fdo so, forcing many shipping companies
OL,13,Fto suspend operations in the area.
OL,15,FUS president Donald Trump floated the
OL,16,Fidea of escorting oil tankers through
OL,17,Fthe Strait of Hormuz with the US Navy.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
